What customers ask about our aged Facebook Pages, verification badges, and related services.

### What are Aged Facebook Pages?

Aged Facebook Pages are Pages that have been active for a long time. They have history, followers, and trust from Meta, making them much more stable for advertising than new pages.

### How old are GOADS Aged Pages?

Our Aged Pages have various ages, typically from several months to many years old, depending on the package.

### What is the warranty on Aged Pages?

Aged Pages come with a 14-day warranty with unlimited fast & free replacements if disabled under normal usage.

### Can I change Page information and name after purchase?

Yes. You can change the Page name, information, category, and other details after receiving it (depending on Meta's current policy for that page).

### Can I run ads on Aged Pages?

Yes. Aged Pages are excellent for running ads, especially when combined with verified BM and aged profiles.

### Do Aged Pages come with posts or history?

Many of our high-quality Aged Pages include natural history and some posts, which increases trust with Meta.

### Can I add Aged Pages to my Business Manager?

Yes. We can help you add them to your BM or you can do it yourself easily.

### Are Aged Pages clean and safe to use?

Yes. Our Aged Pages are carefully selected and maintained to ensure high stability and low risk of disable.

### What should I do after receiving an Aged Page?

Add it to your verified BM, warm it up gradually with natural activity, and follow our [Security Tips](/docs/questions-bank/security-tips) before running ads.

### Can I use Aged Pages for multiple ad accounts?

Yes. One Aged Page can be used across multiple ad accounts inside your Business Manager.

### Why should I buy Aged Pages?

Aged Pages help improve ad approval rates, increase trust score, and reduce the chance of ad account or BM restrictions.

### What is Verification Badge (Blue Tick)?

Verification Badge is the official blue checkmark from Meta. It increases trust, improves account/page credibility, and can help with better reach and ad performance.

### Why should I use Verification Badge?

The blue tick makes your Page look more professional and trustworthy. It helps increase user confidence, improve organic reach, and makes advertising more effective.

### Does GOADS provide Verification Badge service?

Yes. GOADS provides Verification Badge (Blue Tick) service at very competitive prices.

### Do you provide full Verification Badge for Instagram Pages?

Yes. We offer complete Verification Badge packages for both Facebook Pages and Instagram Pages.

### Can I get custom followers for my Page?

Yes. GOADS provides custom follower services tailored to your needs.

### Why choose GOADS for Aged Pages and Verification?

GOADS has the best page nurturing system in the market. All pages are carefully farmed and maintained for maximum stability and success rate.

